OL,3,CCouncil tax in Scottish Borders to
OL,4,Crise by 8.5%
OL,6,FCouncil tax in the Scottish Borders is
OL,7,Fset to rise by 8.5 per cent from
OL,8,FApril, after councillors voted through
OL,9,Fthe increase.
OL,11,FThis means that if you live in a band
OL,12,FD property, you will pay #1,618.52 per
OL,13,Fyear in council tax - an increase of
OL,14,F#126.88.
OL,16,FBut the move wasn't backed unanimously.
OL,18,FThe Conservative-led administration
OL,19,Finsists the increase is needed to
OL,20,Fprotect local services.
