OL,3,CCouncil tax in Scottish Borders to
OL,4,Crise by 8.5%
OL,6,FScottish Borders Council leader Cllr
OL,7,FEuan Jardine said: "We're maintaining
OL,8,Fand delivering services for the people
OL,9,Fof the Borders who wanted that -
OL,10,Fpeople did say they wouldn't mind
OL,11,Fcouncil tax going up to maintain those.
OL,13,F"A lot of the time it's things you
OL,14,Fdon't see that the council tax is
OL,15,Ffunding, like the social care budget.
OL,17,F"We have an elderly population and we
OL,18,Fneed to look after those, and the cost
OL,19,Fof care is going up.
