OL,3,CCouncil tax in Scottish Borders to
OL,4,Crise by 8.5%
OL,6,FCllr Thornton-Nicol proposed a 350%
OL,7,Fcouncil tax levy on long term empty
OL,8,Fand second homes - which she said
OL,9,Fwould help tackle the housing crisis
OL,10,Fand generate an extra 1.2million
OL,11,Fpounds.
OL,13,FThe current budget sees owners of
OL,14,Fempty homes facing a 300% levy on the
OL,15,Fbase level of council tax - up from
OL,16,F200%. And holiday home owners will
OL,17,Fhave to pay 225%.
OL,19,FBut the amendment failed to garner
OL,20,Fsupport - and was defeated 23 votes to
OL,21,F8, with one abstention.
