OL,10,Fpublic ahead of an election.
OL,12,FHe said there was a lack of
OL,13,Funderstanding of the 'serious budget
OL,14,Fconstraints' the local authority was
OL,15,Funder - a sentiment backed by several
OL,16,Fothers in the chamber.
